OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1777295491
OL,3,C'Powerhouse' journalist Jim McDowell
OL,4,Cremembered after death aged 76
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to
OL,7,F"powerhouse" journalist Jim McDowell,
OL,8,Fwho has died aged 76.
OL,10,FMr McDowell was northern editor of the
OL,11,FSunday World for 25 years, and worked
OL,12,Fin journalism in Northern Ireland for
OL,13,Fnearly half a century.
OL,15,FHe was a lead campaigner for justice
OL,16,Fin the case of Martin O'Hagan, a
OL,17,FSunday World reporter who was shot
OL,18,Fdead by loyalists in Lurgan, Co
OL,19,FArmagh, in September 2001; and Mr
OL,20,FMcDowell himself also received death
OL,21,Fthreats from loyalist paramilitaries.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
