FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1777295491
OL,3,C'Powerhouse' journalist Jim McDowell
OL,4,Cremembered after death aged 76
OL,6,FHis funeral notice read: "Until the
OL,7,Fend, you were the bravest of the
OL,8,Fbrave. Legend."
OL,10,FPatrick Corrigan, head of nations &
OL,11,Fregions at AmnestyUK, shared a picture
OL,12,Fof Mr McDowell taken in the Duke of
OL,13,FYork pub in Belfast, a bar known for
OL,14,Fits link to journalists.
OL,16,F"(Mr McDowell) shared the traumatic
OL,17,Fnight of the murder of his friend and
OL,18,FSunday World colleague Martin O'Hagan,
OL,19,Fand the many times they were attacked
OL,20,Fand threatened," Mr Corrigan wrote on
OL,21,FX.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUpD@OO]xD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
