PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1777295491
OL,3,C'Powerhouse' journalist Jim McDowell
OL,4,Cremembered after death aged 76
OL,6,FUTV's Sharon O'Neill described
OL,7,FMrMcDowell as one of the best in the
OL,8,Fbusiness 'and a top guy too'.
OL,10,FBBC community correspondent Mark
OL,11,FSimpson said on social media: "I
OL,12,Flooked up to Jim McDowell. In every
OL,13,Fway. Brave. Brilliant. Best of
OL,14,FBelfast. He loved the city.
OL,16,F"First met him at CIYMS rugby club (he
OL,17,Fused to say CIYMS stood for Come In
OL,18,FYour Ma's Shouting). Learned from him
OL,19,Fat City Hall (Dome of Delight) Belfast
OL,20,Fhas lost a giant of journalism."
OL,26,@sD@_OUxD@AOU|D@`O]
