OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1777295491
OL,3,C'Powerhouse' journalist Jim McDowell
OL,4,Cremembered after death aged 76
OL,6,FBBC radio presenter Stephen Nolan
OL,7,Fdescribed Mr McDowell as "a powerhouse
OL,8,Fof personality and integrity".
OL,10,F"I am so sad to hear we have lost one
OL,11,Fof Northern Ireland's best, and most
OL,12,Fcolourful journalists," he posted on X.
OL,14,FBBC producer and journalist Karen
OL,15,FEnglish wrote: "Jim was a unique one
OL,16,Fof a kind journalism powerhouse. A
OL,17,Ftowering personality, his impact and
OL,18,Finfluence resonated far and wide.
OL,20,F"Thinking of his wife Lindy, daughter
OL,21,FFaye and sons Jamie and Micah."
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@]O]rD@AOUtD@WO]wD@POU|D@AOU}D@
